data.description: Fantastic Investment Property or Family Home off prestigious treelined El Dorado Parkway less than 3 miles to Cape Coral Yacht Club and Downtown Cape Coral Entertainment Center. 3/2/2 plus a separate 1/1 kitchenette mother-in-law suite or rental. Oversized 1/3rd acre fenced corner lot with circular drive complimented by oversized 2+car garage. Huge Island Kitchen featuring solid wood cabinetry and New Premium Stainless Steel Appliances adjacent to a dream 11 X 10 Utility laundry room. Impressive 15 x 11 Master Suite with attached master en suite includes large walk-in closet, large patio slider to HUGE  21 x 10 lanai plus bonus transom window. Separate Mother in Law Suite or rental features large 14 x 11 Kitchenette/Family room and a HUGE 16 X 11 Master Bedroom and separate Central AC System is currently being rented for $750.00/mo and tenant would LOVE to stay after conveyance . Very well established neighborhood where..."everybody knows everybody". ALL ASSESSMENTS PAID IN FULL! QUALIFIES FOR AMERICAN HOME SHIELD WARRANTY.
